        <description>&lt;p&gt;Notes on responsive design testing&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;testing-your-responsive-design&#34;&gt;Testing your responsive design&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the built-in tools in Safari &amp;amp; Chrome, you can test your website&amp;rsquo;s responsive design and preview its effects on different device.
Apart from the common aspect ratios such as 16:9 (For desktop/non-Apple tablets), 4:3 (iPad), ~20:9 (iPhone), some new aspect ratios for foldable phones could also take into consideration when coding your responsive design.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;testing-responsive-design-on-chrome&#34;&gt;Testing Responsive Design on Chrome&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To test your design using Chrome you may simply hit F12 or right click anywhere on your webpage and hit inspect.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://felix-ku.github.io/p/responsive-design-testing/img1.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1283&#34;
	height=&#34;910&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://felix-ku.github.io/p/responsive-design-testing/img1_huf3572309ba7f321f6cd58be9c1685d4c_145804_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://felix-ku.github.io/p/responsive-design-testing/img1_huf3572309ba7f321f6cd58be9c1685d4c_145804_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;&amp;ldquo;Inspect Option in right-click menu&amp;rdquo;&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;140&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;338px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click the icon beside the &amp;ldquo;Element&amp;rdquo; text label&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://felix-ku.github.io/p/responsive-design-testing/2.png&#34;
	width=&#34;404&#34;
	height=&#34;197&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://felix-ku.github.io/p/responsive-design-testing/2_hu1bb9fba7eb9ae78d98a39c8131defa93_33133_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://felix-ku.github.io/p/responsive-design-testing/2_hu1bb9fba7eb9ae78d98a39c8131defa93_33133_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;Click icon&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;205&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;492px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That&amp;rsquo;s it! You may now test out your design and choose the target device in the upper menu&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://felix-ku.github.io/p/responsive-design-testing/3.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1276&#34;
	height=&#34;910&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://felix-ku.github.io/p/responsive-design-testing/3_hu30e2bea467e1a51586f5586a0bba0e17_294569_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://felix-ku.github.io/p/responsive-design-testing/3_hu30e2bea467e1a51586f5586a0bba0e17_294569_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;Choose your target device&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;140&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;336px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You may also add custom device for special aspect ratio&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://felix-ku.github.io/p/responsive-design-testing/4.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1289&#34;
	height=&#34;910&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://felix-ku.github.io/p/responsive-design-testing/4_hu95fc628e0ef9bc53fb16d433c67d2b4e_128357_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://felix-ku.github.io/p/responsive-design-testing/4_hu95fc628e0ef9bc53fb16d433c67d2b4e_128357_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
